{
  "stem": "10587.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were 10 children.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And many of the-- of my father's brothers, which were my uncles, used to pay-- my grandfather used to pay other people to go to the army.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then they-- they-- when it came down to my father, because the older brothers, they-- they couldn't do it anymore.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they did all sorts of things, you know, to themselves.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One cut his finger off, and one lit his-- one did something with the eyes, which from this he contracted tuberculosis, and he died-- died of that.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So my father said he's not going to do anything.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He-- he was drafted during World War I.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he served-- he was an officer in the cavalry.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they-- and he-- he also was three years in Siberia, because his regiment was storming Kiev.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He used to tell us stories of his experience, life experience.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was very interesting because he-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] when they stormed Kiev, the-- the Russians were yelling, [SPEAKING RUSSIAN], which means, run for your life, the Germans are coming.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So instead of running away, they ran around them and circled them and them, and-- and took the whole regiment to prison in Siberia.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he had-- he himself had quite an experience, and he was-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] he-- he was given some medal of distinction for his service.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Which during the war, the Wehrmacht at the beginning, used to-- when my father used to show them the passport with the Polish Austrian military papers, they used to salute him and say, [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You can go back home.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
